name: "complete me" a book of lines (SOLD OUT)
description: "complete me" is a diy fine art coloring book. It consists of 12 pages filled with some of my favorite original inkings. The contents are black outlines thatIi used to make various products including t-shirts and prints. The book is meant to be used however you so please. You can color in it with crayons,acrylics,oils,pastels,colored pencils,ink,pens,markers or any medium you see fit, watercolor will smear ink. or you can just leave it as a coffee table book, remove the pages and frame them. Each page is perforoated for easy removal. Each page is printed on 90 lb italian watercolor paper, cover is 100lb felt linen. This book is very limited edition of 20. Each page is slightly smaller than 8"x10". Signed and numbered By Jared Wright. all orders ship wednesday august 29th and come with free stickers and some will receive original doodles!
